
hotcolormap(1)                 Scilab Function                 hotcolormap(1)
NAME
  hotcolormap - Yellow to red  RGB colormap

CALLING SEQUENCE
  cmap=hotcolormap(n)

PARAMETERS

  n         : an integer greater or equal than 3, the "colormap" size

  cmap      : matrix with 3 column, [R,G,B] color definition

DESCRIPTION
  Computes a colormap with hots colors varying from red to yellow

SEE ALSO
  colormap, xset, plot3d1, graycolormap

EXAMPLE
  xset('colormap',hotcolormap(32))
  plot3d1()
